Interface StatementBuffer.IWrittenSPOArray

  • Type Parameters:
    S -
    Enclosing class:
    StatementBuffer<S extends org.openrdf.model.Statement>

    public static interface StatementBuffer.IWrittenSPOArray
    Note: The use of this interface is NOT encouraged. It is used to hook the axioms in BaseAxioms. Ideally this could be backed out in favor of using the IChangeLog but I was not able to make that work out very easily.
    Author:
    bryan
    See Also:
    BLZG-1552

    • Method Detail

      • didWriteSPOs

        void didWriteSPOs(SPO[] stmts,
                  int numStmts)
        A callback that is invoked with the statements actually written onto the backing store. The default implementation is a NOP.
        Parameters:
        stmts - An array of the statements written onto the backing store.
        numStmts - The number of entries in that array that were written.
